reviewText: This is a nice music video to put on and listen to when you are not sitting in front of the television.  I like the music and performers.
very good music & service.....very good follow through.  everything was just as requested. I would not hesitate to order again.

Loved it,..but it would have been nice if a 'graphic' could have been on screen telling WHO the groups were. We loved the fact that there were no commercials.

I'll give it a B+ for listening and a C+ for watching.  Not all original groups or at least a member of group. But, fairly good imitations and originals as good as ever.

Not great quality video or sound, but really interesting to see the stars.  Judging by their appearance, it looks like it was taped in the early 70's--the other video that goes with it was taped at the same time, because it was the same place, people and clothing.  I enjoyed watching them both.
